{"tid":604815,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"NBA季後賽討論區","createTime":"2018-03-25T06:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T14:17:54.000Z","uid":173674,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d2690781b148fc1fa6f601b5e04f2e704ba08a54","tid":604815,"uid":173674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T06:05:37.000Z","msg":"常規賽都就尼打完，大家都應該有自己既心水球隊/matchup, 所以想同大家理性交流下。先講東岸，睇下大家反應先再講埋西岸<br />\n<br />\n東岸心水：Boston Celtics <br />\n<br />\n1. 雖然Hayward 傷左，但比左好多機會比Jaylen Brown 同Tatum成長。而兩位小將都射到3分，又守到波，唔會輕易比對手打到mismatch<br />\n2. 板凳夠深, 好似Marcus Smart, Monroe 同Rozier 出到尼打到good defence<br />\n3. 有irving 呢個屈機得分點，關鍵時刻有人可以射到clutch shot<br />\n4. Brad Steven 有料，好多時叫完timeout之後球隊都有明顯反彈（之前佢教大學果陣用殘陣都打到識飛咁）<br />\n5. 成隊波心態好，好勝心強，戰術執行性高"},{"pid":"4c0d68e015771e8db40a4f37f5e288ea8dc2ab05","tid":604815,"uid":135607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T11:37:38.000Z","msg":"祖雲達斯有機贏歐聯"},{"pid":"0c83fb9b2ae1032decf02d998a1fdfaf48a6d846","tid":604815,"uid":7837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c0d68e015771e8db40a4f37f5e288ea8dc2ab05","tid":604815,"uid":135607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T11:37:38.000Z","msg":"祖雲達斯有機贏歐聯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T14:17:54.000Z","msg":"🤔"}]}